'Betty' B.Boppin is a pirate found aboard the Lady Zay. To be able to access the ship, you must have reached a certain point in Lunar Diplomacy. He plays a small role in the quest.

Dialogue[edit | edit source]

This article on an NPC has an associated dialogue page.
Click here for a transcript of possible conversations with this NPC.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • His name may be a reference to Betty Boop, a famous cartoon character from the 1930s.
  • It may also be a reference to the Bebop style of music.
